properties.Name: CustomerAccountChannelProductSummary
properties.Description: A summary of customer account transactions via the associated channel for the associated product for the period.

Columns.Name: CustomerAccountId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Customer Account.

Columns.Name: ChannelId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Channel.

Columns.Name: ProductId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Product.

Columns.Name: PeriodStartDate
Columns.Description: The period start date for which the information is calculated.

Columns.Name: PeriodEndDate
Columns.Description: The period end date for which the information is calculated.

Columns.Name: NumberOfChannelProductTransactions
Columns.Description: The number of channel product transaction for the period.

Columns.Name: QuantityOfProductSold
Columns.Description: The quantity of product sold via the associated channel during the period.

Columns.Name: ValueOfProductSold
Columns.Description: The valuation or amount of product sold via the channel to the customer account during the associated period.

Columns.Name: QuantityOfProductDistributed
Columns.Description: The quantity of product distributed via the associated channel during the period.

Columns.Name: ValueOfProductDistributed
Columns.Description: The valuation or amount of product distributed via the channel to the customer account during the associated period.
